@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_sqplbc(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = v2
    v1 = v0
    v0 = tmp
    tmp = 0.63
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.sin((v0 + 0.14 / v2 + 0.61)))
    v0 = (0.15 / (wp.abs(v0 + 1.00) / 0.95))
    v0 = ((v1 / (v0 + 0.61 + v1 + 0.02)) - ((v0 + 0.60 * v1 + 0.79) / (v1 + 0.61 - v2 + 0.02)))
    v1 = (wp.cos((v0 + 0.62 + v0 + 0.93)) * wp.cos(wp.exp(v0 + 1.00)))
    data[tid] = v0
